cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.SD, cs.IR 

This paper is about natural language understanding in intelligent personal digital assistants (IPDAs), which is a popular application of artificial intelligence. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the sub-categories of computational linguistics (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also proposes a set of efficient and scalable models for domain classification, which involves information retrieval (cs.IR) and potentially system design (cs.SD).
